celestia.desc: Celestia is the first modular blockchain network. It is a modular consensus and data network, built to enable anyone to easily deploy their own blockchain with minimal overhead.
celestia.installBin:

rm -rf celestia-app 
git clone https://github.com/celestiaorg/celestia-app.git

APP_VERSION=v1.0.0-rc10

make install
cd $HOME
rm -rf networks
git clone https://github.com/celestiaorg/networks.git

cp $HOME/networks/mocha/genesis.json $HOME/.celestia-app/config

git clone https://github.com/celestiaorg/celestia-app.git

lava.installBin:
cd $HOME
rm -rf $HOME/lava
git clone https://github.com/lavanet/lava.git
cd lava
git checkout v0.21.1.2
make install
lava.newInstallBin:
sudo systemctl stop lavad
cd $HOME
echo "export LAVA_CHAIN_ID="lava-testnet-2"" >> $HOME/.bash_profile
source $HOME/.bash_profile
cp $HOME/.lava/config/priv_validator_key.json $HOME/priv_validator_key.json_backup
cp $HOME/.lava/config/node_key.json $HOME/node_key.json_backup
lavad tendermint unsafe-reset-all
wget -O $HOME/.lava/config/genesis.json https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lavanet/lava-config/main/testnet-2/genesis_json/genesis.json
wget https://github.com/lavanet/lava/releases/download/v0.21.1.2/lavad-v0.21.1.2-linux-amd64
chmod +x lavad-v0.21.1.2-linux-amd64
sed -i \
  -e 's/timeout_commit = ".*"/timeout_commit = "30s"/g' \
  -e 's/timeout_propose = ".*"/timeout_propose = "1s"/g' \
  -e 's/timeout_precommit = ".*"/timeout_precommit = "1s"/g' \
  -e 's/timeout_precommit_delta = ".*"/timeout_precommit_delta = "500ms"/g' \
  -e 's/timeout_prevote = ".*"/timeout_prevote = "1s"/g' \
  -e 's/timeout_prevote_delta = ".*"/timeout_prevote_delta = "500ms"/g' \
  -e 's/timeout_propose_delta = ".*"/timeout_propose_delta = "500ms"/g' \
  -e 's/skip_timeout_commit = ".*"/skip_timeout_commit = false/g' \
  -e 's/seeds = ".*"/seeds = "3a445bfdbe2d0c8ee82461633aa3af31bc2b4dc0@testnet2-seed-node.lavanet.xyz:26656,e593c7a9ca61f5616119d6beb5bd8ef5dd28d62d@testnet2-seed-node2.lavanet.xyz:26656"/g' \
  $HOME/.lava/config/config.toml
sed -i -e 's/broadcast-mode = ".*"/broadcast-mode = "sync"/g' $HOME/.lava/config/config.toml
sudo mv $HOME/lavad-v0.21.1.2-linux-amd64 $(which lavad)
lava.desc: Lava pairs Providers with Applications for scalable, private and uncensored access to Web3.
lava.newInit:
cd $HOME 
curl -s https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lavanet/lava-config/main/testnet-2/genesis_json/genesis.json > $HOME/.lava/config/genesis.json 
curl -Ls https://lava-binary-upgrades.s3.amazonaws.com/testnet-2/cosmovisor-upgrades/cosmovisor-upgrades.zip > cosmovisor-upgrades.zip 
unzip cosmovisor-upgrades.zip 
rm cosmovisor-upgrades.zip 
sed -i \   
-e 's/timeout_commit = ".*"/timeout_commit = "30s"/g' \   
-e 's/timeout_propose = ".*"/timeout_propose = "1s"/g' \  
-e 's/timeout_precommit = ".*"/timeout_precommit = "1s"/g' \   -e 's/timeout_precommit_delta = ".*"/timeout_precommit_delta = "500ms"/g' \   
-e 's/timeout_prevote = ".*"/timeout_prevote = "1s"/g' \   
-e 's/timeout_prevote_delta = ".*"/timeout_prevote_delta = "500ms"/g' \   
-e 's/timeout_propose_delta = ".*"/timeout_propose_delta = "500ms"/g' \   
-e 's/skip_timeout_commit = ".*"/skip_timeout_commit = false/g' \   
-e 's/seeds = ".*"/seeds = "3a445bfdbe2d0c8ee82461633aa3af31bc2b4dc0@testnet2-seed-node.lavanet.xyz:26656,e593c7a9ca61f5616119d6beb5bd8ef5dd28d62d@testnet2-seed-node2.lavanet.xyz:26656"/g' \   $HOME/.lava/config/config.toml 
sed -i -e 's/broadcast-mode = ".*"/broadcast-mode = "sync"/g' $HOME/.lava/config/config.toml 
sudo mv $HOME/cosmovisor-upgrades/genesis/bin/lavad $HOME/go/bin/lavad
lavad init "test" --chain-id lava-testnet-2
